  "prompt": "What is Roadrunner Technical Support?",
  "response": "Roadrunner Technical Support was a customer service and technical assistance service provided by Time Warner Cable (now Spectrum) for their internet, cable, and phone services. As part of the cable company's support system, they helped customers troubleshoot issues with their internet connectivity, cable television, and telephone services. However, with the merger of Time Warner Cable into Spectrum in 2016, the specific \"Roadrunner\" branding has largely been phased out, and technical support is now typically provided under the Spectrum brand.",
